A Basecame theme for Redmine.

Modified to support small display size. Optimised for mobile devices with screen width equal 480px.

INSTALL
-------

To install, just clone into your Redmine theme dir like so:

    $ cd /path/to/redmine/public/themes
    $ git clone http://github.com/MartinSenovsky/redmine-basecamp-theme-responsive.git basecamp-responsive
